headline: Senator Warren Has a New Target on Wall Street: Private Credit
summary: Sen. Elizabeth Warren sent letters Thursday to agencies including S&P Global Ratings, Moody’s Ratings and Fitch Ratings, asking for information about how they score the riskiness of private-credit products.
